text: Lee Won-gyu (born 13 October 1993) is a South Korean sport shooter. He participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a medal.300 m team standard rifle results ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:South Korean male sport shooters Category:ISSF rifle shooters Category:Shooters at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for South Korea Category:Asian Games medalists in shooting Category:Universiade bronze medalists for South Korea Category:Universiade medalists in shooting Category:Medalists at the 2015 Summer Universiade
